	‚Ä¢	Pros
	‚Ä¢	Stable
	‚Ä¢	Easy to understand
	‚Ä¢	Widely used

	‚Ä¢	Cons
	‚Ä¢	Centralized
	‚Ä¢	Requires trust in issuer
2Ô∏è. Crypto-Collateralized Stablecoins
üîπ How they work
	‚Ä¢	Backed by cryptocurrency
	‚Ä¢	Over-collateralized to manage volatility
	‚Ä¢	Managed by smart contracts
üîπ Example
