	‚Ä¢	Complex
	‚Ä¢	Risk during market crashes
3Ô∏è. Algorithmic Stablecoins ‚ö†Ô∏è (High risk)
üîπ How they work
	‚Ä¢	No direct collateral
	‚Ä¢	Use algorithms & supply control
	‚Ä¢	Mint/burn tokens to maintain peg
