	‚Ä¢	Peg breaks during panic
	‚Ä¢	No real backing
4Ô∏è. Commodity-Backed Stablecoins
üîπ Backed by
	‚Ä¢	Gold
	‚Ä¢	Oil
	‚Ä¢	Other real assets
